{"tid":1778781,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"RPG Maker系列 (MV, VX ace)","createTime":"2019-12-11T08:13:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-08T14:59:06.000Z","uid":123323,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"45cd01cbb9656d51bd7a572d46a6b81454beb934","tid":1778781,"uid":123323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T08:13:18.000Z","msg":"其實香港本地有冇RPG Maker嘅交流group之類嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最近由0開始學點用RPG Maker系列嘅software, 基本用法等等<br />\n<br />\n為咗整到自己嘅RPG game, 小弟最近都甘願學電繪去自製 characters, tileset etc.<br />\n<br />\n生活雖然頗為忙碌，小弟都識少少programming嘢，亦都肯學肯做肯去了解<br />\n<br />\n但係冇交流group咁孤怜怜一個人作戰又真係好苦悶，我唔想自己對RPG maker嘅熱誠慢慢咁冇撚咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7b20d4d7600cc4211be07fb8aa85ac268c34852","tid":1778781,"uid":12468,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T08:17:52.000Z","msg":"乜都唔識推一推"},{"pid":"047dd06c427745f13eca43948730ba7cb9abd91e","tid":1778781,"uid":123323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T09:03:21.000Z","msg":"或者遲啲我考慮下開個大post介紹下RPG Maker，揾吓有冇同好嘅人係有上連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為我肯定孤軍作戰RPG Maker嘅人都幾多吓 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53087a8f2f73176acd153f989396ffb203c024ee","tid":1778781,"uid":101706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T02:52:30.000Z","msg":"我有整 未整完之後停咗係到好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf5c0bf8d3785e9ef1581d3f1bd975ffd03294e6","tid":1778781,"uid":54332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T03:29:48.000Z","msg":"留名跟進<br />\n以前成日整"},{"pid":"a41a5274ff347b535fbe035cb8a0e3721b86ee1c","tid":1778781,"uid":243216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T03:31:59.000Z","msg":"n年玩過，但整完自己都覺得唔好玩，好快就棄咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif