8:08:50.000Z","msg":"狂父 同埋 魔女之家 真係正到喊<br />\n唔知大家有冇玩？<br />\n我只係睇人直播玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"119b54b4d822ad30fe7e94b5387f007ded301245","tid":1778781,"uid":90259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T06:22:42.000Z","msg":"留名跟進<br />\n以前有個yanfly好有心機，share好多script俾人，仲要免費，上youtube可以睇到係乜都有包<br />\n不過依家冇做，作者覺得俾心機時間付出冇回報<br />\n仲發現香港有人將佢哋啲script打包賣錢，意興闌珊"},{"pid":"13ee6290a2efc3fed71a29bc8dd05e60d4696952","tid":1778781,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T09:24:16.000Z","msg":"以前用過XP定2000，留名"},{"pid":"12e5145f5bbfe473f90e7217368d0345a13b555d","tid":1778781,"uid":23764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T10:14:28.000Z","msg":"有係steam買左rpg maker,但買完之後冇整過，唔知點整，乜要用到java既咩？我學緊java,但未勁到可以拎來整game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8b46d01221e2d4ed04c9f258a658d8266b629df","tid":1778781,"uid":123323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"119b54b4d822ad30fe7e94b5387f007ded301245","tid":1778781,"uid":90259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T06:22:42.000Z","msg":"留名跟進<br />\n以前有個yanfly好有心機，share好多script俾人，仲要免費，上youtube可以睇到係乜都有包<br />\n不過依家冇做，作者覺得俾心機時間付出冇回報<br />\n仲發現香港有人將佢哋啲script打包賣錢，意興闌珊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T18:04:21.000Z","msg":"啱啱開始研究RPG Maker唔知原來有呢件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好偉大<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1be08b0449ee8ed6a231d332b9d91c4586457504","tid":1778781,"uid":123323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12e5145f5bbfe473f90e7217368d0345a13b555d","tid":1778781,"uid":23764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T10:14:28.000Z","msg":"有係steam買左rpg maker,但買完之後冇整過，唔知點整，乜要用到java既咩？我學緊java,但未勁到可以拎來整game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T18:10:34.000Z","msg":"唔使java都得<br />\n不過有好多功能或者System本身RPG Maker, 冇辦法之下就要自己寫script<br />\n<br />\n例如牧場物語咁，你需要一個遊戲自己獨有嘅Time &amp; Day System, 天氣嗰啲點樣random法又要自己寫<br />\n<br />\n種花種菜又可以寫script紀錄下每棵植物parameter: 生命值, 生長度，營養，水分，幾時發芽出果實等等<br />\n<br />\n唔用script直接用switch/if-else statement去做會好痛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cf4f8cd71e80f6ff8989b5a075e49dba229c6c2","tid":1778781,"uid":90259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d8b46d01221e2d4ed04c9f258a658d8266b629df","tid":1778781,"uid":123323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"119b54b4d822ad30fe7e94b5387f007ded301245","tid":1778781,"uid":90259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T06:22:42.000Z","msg":"留名跟進<br />\n以前有個yanfly好有心機，share好多script俾人，仲要免費，上youtube可以睇到係乜都有包<br />\n不過依家冇做，作者覺得俾心機時間付出冇回報<br />\n仲發現香港有人將佢哋啲script打包賣錢，意興闌珊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T18:04:21.000Z","msg":"啱啱開始研究RPG Maker唔知原來有呢件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好偉大<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T18:41:17.000Z","msg":"佢哋依家冇再更新，啲plugin變番收錢，不過都好似幾舊水有齊全部，過十萬行script咁嘅價錢差唔多係送咁濟<br />\n可以youtube Yanfly Engine睇佢介紹，如果啱用就上patreon俾錢支持下，當課金好買個DLC好，MV啲垃圾圖都收得貴過佢<br />\n<br />\n大部分plugin好多人譯成中文又發一次，但唔好貪方便去其他地方copy<br />\n佢真係好有心，以前連plugin之間嘅相容都搞埋<br />\n上steam睇好多rpg maker game 都有用佢啲plugin <br />\n無奈世上太多仆街<br />\n只可以講佢Not the hero we deserves, But the hero we needed.<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb0fa6ddfc6c121d17289a0ee1c85f6407bbf00c","tid":1778781,"uid":66191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T23:46:47.000Z","msg":"竟然有同好<br />\n開GROUP 記住預埋我<br />\n利申:搞左好耐都未搞到一隻GAME"},{"pid":"67fbd5229f3f76702c36e580d118e0aa4b5592f2","tid":1778781,"uid":66191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"45cd01cbb9656d51bd7a572d46a6b81454beb934","tid":1778781,"uid":123323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":