me":"2019-12-17T20:36:28.000Z","msg":"有人覆呢個post已經好慶幸 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係按照呢個人數，就算開discord/tg似會係死城咁樣冇聲氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\ngroup就暫時唔開了，除非可以成風氣"},{"pid":"382419f90e47fdcb75088e571f017ecb8fd4431d","tid":1778781,"uid":123323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb0fa6ddfc6c121d17289a0ee1c85f6407bbf00c","tid":1778781,"uid":66191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T23:46:47.000Z","msg":"竟然有同好<br />\n開GROUP 記住預埋我<br />\n利申:搞左好耐都未搞到一隻GAME"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T20:40:11.000Z","msg":"group呢啲嘢等到有夠多人先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n始終大家嘅熱情，興趣都重要<br />\n<br />\n我都開始掌握更多嘅基本操作，但唔期望現階段寫到game<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n嫌自己付出時間仲未夠班去到自發隻game既能力"},{"pid":"0c6e793ddf5a59bb1fc73b60564573e97629ea9d","tid":1778781,"uid":123323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0cf4f8cd71e80f6ff8989b5a075e49dba229c6c2","tid":1778781,"uid":90259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d8b46d01221e2d4ed04c9f258a658d8266b629df","tid":1778781,"uid":123323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"119b54b4d822ad30fe7e94b5387f007ded301245","tid":1778781,"uid":90259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T06:22:42.000Z","msg":"留名跟進<br />\n以前有個yanfly好有心機，share好多script俾人，仲要免費，上youtube可以睇到係乜都有包<br />\n不過依家冇做，作者覺得俾心機時間付出冇回報<br />\n仲發現香港有人將佢哋啲script打包賣錢，意興闌珊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T18:04:21.000Z","msg":"啱啱開始研究RPG Maker唔知原來有呢件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好偉大<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T18:41:17.000Z","msg":"佢哋依家冇再更新，啲plugin變番收錢，不過都好似幾舊水有齊全部，過十萬行script咁嘅價錢差唔多係送咁濟<br />\n可以youtube Yanfly Engine睇佢介紹，如果啱用就上patreon俾錢支持下，當課金好買個DLC好，MV啲垃圾圖都收得貴過佢<br />\n<br />\n大部分plugin好多人譯成中文又發一次，但唔好貪方便去其他地方copy<br />\n佢真係好有心，以前連plugin之間嘅相容都搞埋<br />\n上steam睇好多rpg maker game 都有用佢啲plugin <br />\n無奈世上太多仆街<br />\n只可以講佢Not the hero we deserves, But the hero we needed.<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T20:41:59.000Z","msg":"啱啱見到最新video話retiring permanently <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實係咪香港人嚟，其他tutorial video幾高質，可惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f722b1b42a8fc89366902c3bebacb0b10992ff85","tid":1778781,"uid":105822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T02:53:37.000Z","msg":"之前玩過下<br />\n不過自己無美術天份又唔識寫劇本<br />\n就無心機繼續搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算用番內置素材, 人地都可以起到好靚既地圖<br />\n自己就砌到鬼5馬6"},{"pid":"78a6e684cadbc1faba953e77a089e308c3970a6b","tid":1778781,"uid":99607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T02:56:33.000Z","msg":"之前玩過下 <br />\n自己9玩係幾過癮<br />\n但如果你話要上大台<br />\n一定要好有耐性同心機<br />\n諗故事 背景都夠R頭<br />\n未計 要裝啲插件可以令佢戰鬥元素提升<br />\n一定要裝好多Mod  本身佢個程式係好基本"},{"pid":"6b8f6e480040dfdce7f5322da47593d40ff4e52d","tid":1778781,"uid":54332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9cfd8faf676b4acec06627cb2aec850d8accdfa4","tid":1778781,"uid":123323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf5c0bf8d3785e9ef1581d3f1bd975ffd03294e6","tid":1778781,"uid":54332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T03:29:48.000Z","msg":"留名跟進<br />\n以前成日整"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T15:53:00.000Z","msg":"唔好放棄啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當初嘅熱誠去咗邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然睇怕似係香港人生活忙碌係主要原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T23:10:32.000Z",